# Changelog
All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/)

## [Released]
## [1.0.0] - 2021-6-3
### Added
- Change the color of the control buttons to blue;
- Add two more kinds of tetriminos;
- Add "Have fun!" at the beginning of the game;
- Adjust the mechanism such that each time a line is full, not only that line is cleared up but also the line below it, if it exists;

